<p>Cuoco has also voiced and executive produced the beloved animated series Harley Quinn on the DC Universe streaming service.</p>

<p>Her sister Briana also voices Batgirl and several other minor characters in Harley Quinn, and she is featured in multiple episodes of The Flight Attendant as well.</p>

<p>Kaley is also attached to star in the upcoming film The Man From Toronto, starring alongside Kevin Hart and Woody Harrelson. </p>

